szakacs.kpi.fei.tuke.intrfc.arena.game.world

Interface GameWorldPrivileged

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GameWorldBasic, GameWorldUpdatable, ResettableGameClass
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TreasureScooperWorld

    public interface GameWorldPrivileged
extends GameWorldUpdatable, ResettableGameClass
    An extension to the GameWorldUpdatable interface that is exposed to the core backend classes managing the game logic as well as any classes external to the game logic.
